--- src/workspace.js ---
@sig 682b5ff3
export setRoots(roots:Array<{uri: string, name?: string}>)→uri.startsWith,uri.slice,console.error|set workspace root dirs from MCP client (file:// URI or path)
export getWorkspaceRoot()→string→process.cwd|return first workspace root or cwd fallback
export resolvePath(inputPath:string)→string→getWorkspaceRoot,isAbsolute,resolve,resolved.startsWith|resolve relative path to absolute, enforce workspace boundary
PATTERNS: workspace roots set once via MCP initialize|resolvePath prevents directory traversal attacks
EDGE_CASES: file:// URIs auto-stripped to path|absolute paths outside workspace rejected|empty roots fall back to process.cwd()
